{{Note|It's also possible to load the firmware from the userspace.}}

===== Installing the firmware =====

When installing the firmware you can either choose the hardware specific package {{Package|sys-firmware/iwl7260-ucode}} or the general package {{Package|sys-kernel/linux-firmware}}.

